<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Summary</strong>: When request auditing is enabled in a Couchbase cluster, under very high Views query workload, the view-engine audit message queue may grow unbounded causing the view-engine to crash.</p>
<p class="tableblock"><strong>Workaround</strong>: Disable auditing when Views are present in the cluster.</p></td>
